description: This Portland cart specializes in serving up one of El Salvador's local favorites, the pupusa. This thick tortilla treat come stuffed with beans, cheese, and/or meat. Customers can choose any three ingredients they want to come up with their own uniquely tasty combo!  Make sure you grab an horchata to complement your meal, this sweet milky drink has refreshing hints of cinnamon.
name: Pupuseria La Miguelena
